				<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Lucidia Metaverse, which is in the running for the best crypto presale of 2023, uses the freemium model as its main way to get more users and a more diverse group of users. Taking its cue from Facebook&#8217;s famous slogan, &#8220;It&#8217;s free and will always be,&#8221; Lucidia wants to change the way people use the internet by giving users a taste of its product.</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">How Freemium Works:</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The freemium model has several benefits for organic growth and getting more users:</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Accessible Entry Point: By giving users free access to the metaverse, Lucidia removes barriers to joining the platform and encourages more people to do so.</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Diverse User Base: A freemium model brings in a wider range of users, making the metaverse community more diverse and full of life.</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Organic Growth: As more people join and explore the Lucidia metaverse, the platform&#8217;s services and experiences will naturally grow, which will bring in more users and keep them interested.</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Effective Onboarding: Lucidia makes sure that users can quickly and easily dive into the metaverse and start exploring its potential by putting a high priority on a smooth onboarding process.</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Taking Advantage of the Freemium Trend:</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Forbes says that freemium is now the most popular way to price software, which makes it a good choice for Lucidia as it tries to change the way the internet works. By giving users a free taste of the metaverse, Lucidia hopes to make them want to try more immersive and interesting things on its platform.</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Overall, Lucidia Metaverses&#8217; use of the freemium model makes it a strong candidate for the best crypto presale of 2023, as it focuses on user growth, diversity, and smooth onboarding to drive the growth of its metaverse ecosystem.</span></p>					</div>
